videos.description: Kouat Noi drains a long 3-pointer to get the TCU crowd hyped early in the first half.
videos.headline: Noi drains deep 3 for TCU

videos.description: Ochai Agbaji throws down a big one-handed dunk as Kansas keeps it close with TCU in the first half.
videos.headline: Agbaji throws down one-handed slam

videos.description: Kansas' Quentin Grimes hits a shot to tie the game with TCU at 37-37 at halftime.
videos.headline: Grimes ties game at buzzer

videos.description: Ochai Agbaji throws down the dunk off the inbounds pass as Kansas leads TCU in the second half.
videos.headline: Agbaji dunks off inbounds pass

videos.description: TCU's Kendric Davis gets the and-1 on the crazy layup as the TCU crowd goes wild in the second half.
videos.headline: Davis pulls off crazy and-1

videos.description: Ochai Agbaji hits a big 3-pointer in overtime as Kansas leads TCU by 3 with three and a half minutes to go.
videos.headline: Agbaji drains big 3 in overtime
